<p><strong>Advocacy Committee:</strong><br /> Keeping track of legislation, conducting letter writing campaigns, lobbying legislatures, planning advocacy events, and organizing testimony.</p>
</td>
<td>
<p><img src="images/committees/tech.jpg" alt="tech" /></p>
<p><strong>Technology Committee:</strong><br /> Contributing to the WAPF website and social media, including Facebook and Twitter.</p>
