<tr>
<td>
<p><img src="images/committees/education.jpg" alt="education" /></p>
<p><strong>Education Committee:</strong><br /> Working with the Speaker's Bureau members on conference presentations, speaking engagements, and at seminars on this issue of paternity fraud.</p>
</td>
<td>
<p><img src="images/committees/editorial.jpg" alt="editorial" /></p>
